flowchart TB
    Client[kubectl / HTTP Client] -->|HTTPS Request| APIServer[kube-apiserver]
    
    subgraph KubeAPIServer ["Kubernetes API Server"]
        APIServer --> AuthN[1. Authenticate]
        AuthN --> AuthZ[2. Authorize RBAC]
        AuthZ --> MutateWeb[3. Mutating Admission Webhooks]
        MutateWeb --> SchemaVal[4. OpenAPI Schema Validation]
        SchemaVal --> ValidateWeb[5. Validating Admission Webhooks]
    end

    subgraph StorageEngine ["Storage Backend"]
        ValidateWeb --> Etcd[(etcd Key-Value Store)]
    end

    subgraph Extensibility ["Extensibility Pathways"]
        SchemaVal -.->|Schema definition via CRD| CRDStore[Custom Resource Definition]
        ValidateWeb -.->|External Validation| ExtWebhook[Admission Webhook Service]
        APIServer -.->|API Aggregation| APIService[Custom API Service / Extension API Server]
    end

    classDef core fill:#0f172a,stroke:#38bdf8,color:#fff;
    classDef step fill:#1e293b,stroke:#64748b,color:#f1f5f9;
    classDef ext fill:#1e1b4b,stroke:#818cf8,color:#f1f5f9;
    classDef storage fill:#064e3b,stroke:#34d399,color:#fff;

    class Client,APIServer core;
    class AuthN,AuthZ,MutateWeb,SchemaVal,ValidateWeb step;
    class CRDStore,ExtWebhook,APIService ext;
    class Etcd storage;
